overview: Reece & Reece, Attorneys at Law, aggressively protect our clients’ rights in state courts throughout North Carolina and in administrative hearings before the N.C. Department of Motor Vehicles (DMV). In every case, we strive to deliver the best possible outcome, whether it involves negotiating a favorable plea bargain with the prosecutor or fighting your traffic ticket or criminal charge in court before a judge or jury.
